Thanks [~eepayne] for the patches, not that it's part of your change but since you are already touching this code; it's not necessary to do call getPath for local files in:
{code:java}
// Can't use FileSystem API or we get an infinite loop
// since FileSystem uses Configuration API. Use java.io.File instead.
File file = new File(((Path)resource).toUri().getPath())
 .getAbsoluteFile();
{code}
